text: Nils Allen "Booboo" Stewart Jr. (born January 21, 1994), is an American actor, singer and visual artist. He is known for playing Seth Clearwater in The Twilight Saga, Warpath in X-Men: Days of Future Past, Jay in the Disney television movie series Descendants and Willie in Julie and the Phantoms. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Beverly Hills, California Category:Singers from Los Angeles Category:American artists
